					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13968725#post-4861958</guid>
				<title>Perfect proof of &quot;not all SCPs have to be grimdark&quot;</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13968725/scp-5655#post-4861958</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 04 Jan 2021 14:56:17 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ISNorden</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6966599</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thank $DEITY for a break from killer side effects, world-ending threats, and monthly D-class terminations! Even the Foundation deserves to find an anomaly that's good clean fun (but not -J material) sometimes; the experiment logs were outstandingly well done, especially the &quot;balanced budget&quot; and &quot;better key to happiness&quot; wishes. Upvoted, wish I could legally upvote this skip more&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13968725#post-4861815</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
