				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 04 Jan 2021 11:13:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ihp</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1267048</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Upvoted, but there's one grammar thing:</p> <blockquote> <p>Result: An used copy of Kerplunk</p> </blockquote> <p>Since 'used' has a 'you' sound, it should be &quot;a used copy'; if it was 'unused', which has an 'uh' sound, it would be 'An'. English is a dumb language.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
